text: Eunidia trivitticollis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Pierre Téocchi and Jérôme Sudre in 2002.BioLib.cz - Eunidia trivitticollis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 2002
